{"tid":2254302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"付國豪: 否認「可以打我了」是撩交打 而是希望表達無奈、悲傷、諷刺","createTime":"2020-10-22T17:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T02:20:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db20ac84ee06bf6b1235243603a87e931c47946f","tid":2254302,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）去年8月13日至14日的機場集會期間，任職《環球時報》的內地人付國豪遭示威者包圍，4人否認暴動、非法集結、對他人身體加以嚴重傷害及非法禁錮等5項控罪，案件今日（22日）在區域法院續審。事主付國豪續出庭作供，他承認為了保護自己而隱瞞內地記者身份，又表示在無法脫離險境的情況下，曾說「即管打我，怎樣也好」，並非想邀請別人打架，而是「希望表達一種無奈、悲傷、諷刺。」<br />\n<br />\n影片拍得一名男子向付說：「你不是他媽的記者。你是警察！（You are not fxxking journalist. You are cop）」付表示，句子中的「fxxking」令他感到冒犯，他用英語回答自己不是警察也不是記者。付解釋，之所以要隱瞞來自中國內地記者的身份，是為了保護自己免受傷害，「眾所周知，當時的示威對內地人士攻擊性比較大。據我所知，這件事發生前後，有親內地或來自內地的人被打。」<br />\n<br />\n付續稱，聽到一名男子說：「睇吓佢個袋吖！」由於不同意別人翻找他的背包，於是付用雙手抓住背包，並用英語回答「不要⋯⋯為什麼，為什麼？（No......why, why?）」對方表示，「因為中國內地派人來偽裝記者。（because mainland China sent people to pretend to be journalists）」付國豪在庭上一度糾正傳譯員，字眼上應該是「中國內地」而不是「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078361&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=9c2b2487\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078361&h=6c94872b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078361</a>"},{"pid":"635a00e32a0d442d465fd3601157aa548f5251b4","tid":2254302,"uid":285559,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"你老母係出自關心同問候嘅助語詞，至於冚家鏟係客觀咁形容破碎家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc38519b621ee461e0db044a0e4bb25cc3d65a6e","tid":2254302,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"635a00e32a0d442d465fd3601157aa548f5251b4","tid":2254302,"uid":285559,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"你老母係出自關心同問候嘅助語詞，至於冚家鏟係客觀咁形容破碎家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊問候佢"},{"pid":"31a44bebccee626503029c2686420e4d3688cfb6","tid":2254302,"uid":65289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據我所知，這件事發生前後，有親內地或來自內地的人被打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你仲叫人打你係咪自招嫌疑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0c6acae2c24a61e10cc4b38b8ec026887345b2","tid":2254302,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:49:51.000Z","msg":"明顯係同意其他人可以打佢啦"},{"pid":"1fb4c88db3207cca1575eb4c484f6a5d029c7fb6","tid":2254302,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"叫黑狗係讚佢地忠誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d386b15aaece5d86e0bc360a0ac5df2d3ab4e06a","tid":2254302,"uid":133086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHyYi2E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHyYi2E.gif&h=b8cb24c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18a45bb33ecf12f8ebce3cdc230c9401e195fd05","tid":2254302,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:55:33.000Z","msg":"大陸人有時講嘢真係好撚尷尬同嬲打"},{"pid":"708a610325a215b1b84ba9e714944a9460888869","tid":2254302,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"咁方唐鏡咪好無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"